$!You can take the official practice motorcycle theory tests online for free. You can't practise the hazard perception part with these tests.$!

The practice test screens look similar to the theory test you'll take at the test centre.

[Motorcycle riding theory test: example 1.](http://www.direct.gov.uk/prod_consum_dg/groups/dg_digitalassets/@dg/@en/documents/digitalasset/dg_187182.htm "Take practice motorcycle theory test example 1"){:rel="external"} 

[Motorcycle riding theory test: example 2.](http://www.direct.gov.uk/prod_consum_dg/groups/dg_digitalassets/@dg/@en/documents/digitalasset/dg_187183.htm "Take practice motorcycle theory test example 2"){:rel="external"}
